data.description: 1470sf home w/double garage and outbuilding on 1.55 acres zoned CB-2. High visibility/traffic area w/155' of HWY 2 frontage, two curb cuts and a 22,300+ traffic count. This is an ideal location for a home/business. Inside the house, you'll find a comfortable living space with plenty of room to set up an office, showroom, or retail space. The open floor plan and large windows provide ample natural light and a welcoming atmosphere for customers and employees alike. Outside, the spacious lot offers plenty of room for parking and expansion, so you can grow your business as needed. Whether you're looking to start a new venture or expand an existing one, this property is the perfect place to make it happen. Don't miss out on this rare opportunity to own property just 1/2 block from Super 1. Call Sean Scally 406-360-1652 or your real estate professional. Radon
